OL,3,CNational maternity investigation chair
OL,4,C'remains committed' to spring deadline
OL,6,FThe investigation will focus on 12 NHS
OL,7,Ftrusts including University Hospitals
OL,8,FSussex, East Kent Hospitals and Oxford
OL,9,FUniversity Hospitals.
OL,11,FAs part of the investigation, women
OL,12,Fand families are being asked to share
OL,13,Ftheir experiences in a Call for
OL,14,FEvidence which is open until 17 March
OL,15,F2026.
OL,17,FBaroness Amos says so far the survey
OL,18,Fhas had more than 4,000 responses from
OL,19,Fwomen but she wants more people to
OL,20,Fcome forward.
