OL,3,CNational maternity investigation chair
OL,4,C'remains committed' to spring deadline
OL,6,FShe added: "And I particularly want to
OL,7,Fhear from women and families who
OL,8,Fgenerally don't respond to surveys,
OL,9,Fwho generally don't think that they're
OL,10,Fgoing to be listened to. We want to
OL,11,Fhear about your experience."
OL,13,FThere are two separate surveys, one
OL,14,Ffor women and people who have been
OL,15,Fpregnant and one for other people to
OL,16,Fshare their experiences supporting
OL,17,Fsomeone through pregnancy.
OL,19,FThis could include fathers, non-
OL,20,Fbirthing partners, family members and
OL,21,Ffriends.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
