OL,3,CNational maternity investigation chair
OL,4,C'remains committed' to spring deadline
OL,6,FThe first initial findings will be
OL,7,Fpublished at the end of February with
OL,8,FBaroness Amos committing to publishing
OL,9,Fthe final report in spring.
OL,11,F"It will take a lot of hard work, we
OL,12,Fare working as fast as we can and I
OL,13,Fremain committed to that deadline,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,FBaroness Amos said an action plan will
OL,17,Fbe put in place and recommendations
OL,18,Fwill be implemented across the country.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
