OL,3,CNational maternity investigation chair
OL,4,C'remains committed' to spring deadline
OL,6,FShe said: "This is not just about
OL,7,Fthose individual trusts it's about
OL,8,Fwhat can we do nationally across the
OL,9,Fcountry that can begin to interrupt
OL,10,Fthis pattern that we are seeing across
OL,11,Fthe country."
OL,13,FSome people have been calling for a
OL,14,Fstatutory public inquiry which
OL,15,FBaroness Amos says is something for
OL,16,Fthe Health Secretary Wes Streeting to
OL,17,Flook into.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
