OL,3,CNational maternity investigation chair
OL,4,C'remains committed' to spring deadline
OL,6,FShe said: "It doesn't deliver rapid
OL,7,Fresults, it takes years. So that is a
OL,8,Fdifferent kind of investigation. That
OL,9,Fis not what we are seeking to do."
OL,11,FShe added: "Families have been through
OL,12,Funbelievable trauma.
OL,14,F"I have heard experiences that
OL,15,Ffamilies should not have gone through
OL,16,Fand no families should have to go
OL,17,Fthrough again.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
